{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "f84519c3-52d9-4650-9ed6-693035547ade", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/f84519c3-52d9-4650-9ed6-693035547ade@1.pkg/1772597630771/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597631752", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/f84519c3-52d9-4650-9ed6-693035547ade@1.pkg/1772597630771/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597631752"}, "identifier": "f84519c3-52d9-4650-9ed6-693035547ade", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>本题考查尊重他人的具体表现的相关知识。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&zwnj;A&zwnj;：未经允许</span><span>拍摄他人照片并制作成表情包</span><span>，侵犯肖像权，属于不尊重他人隐私，故A不符合题意；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&zwnj;B&zwnj;：在自习室主动佩戴耳机，体现维护公共学习环境的积极尊重行为，符合</span><span>尊重他人的</span><span>要求，故B符合题意；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&zwnj;C&zwnj;：</span><span>深夜大声</span><span>播放音乐，干扰他人休息权，属于不尊重他人，故C不符合题意；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&zwnj;D&zwnj;：匿名发布未经证实的八卦，违反网络信息伦理，侵犯他人名誉权，属于不尊重他人，故D不符合题意；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>因此，</span><span>本题</span><span>正确答案为</span><span>&zwnj;B&zwnj;。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">（改编）</span><span>青春并不意味着肆意放纵，它还需要我们遵守一些基本规则，不能逾越一些基本界限。以下做法最能体现尊重他人的是（ &nbsp; &nbsp; ）</span></p></div>"